entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have completed Muddle the Meatlumps!
entries.journal_entry_description: Find and sack Meatlump Camps throughout the Galaxy. If you run out of devices, return to Halden Wes at the Corellia Times.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find and loot all safes found in Meatlump Camps throughout the Galaxy.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Find and sack Meatlump Camps throughout the Galaxy.
entries.task02_task_display_string_1: You have looted all Meatlump Safes.
entries.task02_task_display_string_2: You have looted all Meatlump Containers.
entries.task02_task_display_string_3: You have decoded all Meatlump Maps.
entries.task02_task_display_string_4: You have defused all Meatlump Bombs.
entries.task02_task_display_string_5: You have disabled all Meatlump Weapons.
entries.task02_task_display_string_6: You have destroyed all Meatlump Food Supplies.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Halden Wes to report mission completion.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Return to Corellia Times Reporter Halden Wes
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find and loot all locked containers found in Meatlump Camps throughout the Galaxy.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Loot all the Meatlump Locked Containers
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Find and decode instructions regarding targets marked for attack. Maps with this intel may be found at Meatlump Camps throughout the Galaxy.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Find and defuse bombs planted near various technology found in cities and towns throughout the Galaxy.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Find and disable weapons supplies found at Meatlump Camps throughout the Galaxy.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Find and destroy all food supplies found in Meatlump Camps throughout the Galaxy.
